data.description: This two bedroom 3 bath home is move in ready and waiting for you to call it home! What a perfect time of the year to gift yourself a new home! Throughout the main living spaces of the home you will find beautiful engineered hardwood floors. The open concept is very sought after and wonderful for entertaining. In the kitchen you will love the custom oak cabinetry, granite counter tops, glass tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and a large pantry cabinet you won't know what to do without! Enjoy the conveniences of the eat in area that connects to the kitchen and living room. The master bedroom features an attached full bath that has been recently updated as well. Granite vanity top and spacious a shower are wonderful features of this space! You will appreciate the matching features in the main bath that boasts the same granite vanity and recent updates. You will be surprised how well this floor plan flows and if you think you might need even more space you have a full unfinished basement with a finished bath that is ready for you to use for storage or finish into additional living space! Some other features we can't forget to mention are the newer windows and doors, including the garage door. Additionally the 2 car attached garage is a major plus! Outside you will love the country feel, the covered back patio and the detached garage/shop that offers even more space to you to utilize! And the landscaping might not look like much now but just wait until spring! Act now this one won't last long!
